snippet: Richie Ramsay of Scotland and Edoardo Molinari of Italy each shot an eight-under-par 62 in the first round of the European Masters.
abstract: Richie Ramsay of Scotland and Edoardo Molinari of Italy share first-round lead in European Masters golf tournament in Crans-Montana, Switzerland.
lead_paragraph: Richie Ramsay of Scotland and Edoardo Molinari of Italy each shot an eight-under-par 62 in the first round of the European Masters.

headline.main: Ramsay and Molinari Lead European Masters
